The paper deals with entity resolution (ER) which is a problem in database management and falls under the category of cs.DB. The paper also proposes a transfer learning algorithm which involves machine learning techniques and falls under the categories of cs.AI and cs.LG. The paper also discusses the use of similarity scores for ER which is a common technique in information retrieval (IR) and falls under the category of cs.IR. Finally, the paper discusses the use of labeled training data which is a common technique in natural language processing (NLP) and falls under the category of cs.CL.
